    Verse: 20
Tags:
  - God
---
You are related to God as a drop of water is related to the ocean. The drop
and the ocean are not different, they are essentially the same. Except
for one thing -- you cannot sail a ship in a drop of water and you can
sail a billion ships in the ocean.
